{"tid":497017,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"亞視永恆！不死！18 月推出新 APP","createTime":"2017-12-12T10:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T10:07:20.000Z","uid":143760,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0123f0f0954b167bfc381d92d3589999893837","tid":497017,"uid":143760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:00:07.000Z","msg":"在上年4月2日結束廣播的亞洲電視，終於又有新消息傳出。小編收到亞視的採訪邀請，其表示將會在下星期一，舉行記者發佈會。到時除了會宣佈亞洲電視數碼媒體有限公司宣佈正式成立外，並會推出全新的「ATV亞洲電視App」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亞視在電郵表示，除了有「各種精選節目，更全力研發提高用戶與節目互動體驗的功能，務求為客戶打造娛樂新視野！」小編估計，這又將會是OTT廣播的方式。根據之前的消息，亞視重組後，便會以繼續廣播。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pc3mag.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/atv-news_pc3leo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fatv-news_pc3leo.jpg&h=bcc9a358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於記者會詳情，這是關於「亞洲電視數碼媒體有限公司」的成立典禮。屆時，將會進行別開生面的應用程式啟用儀式，更會有一眾著名主持人、藝人等出場，介紹全新應用程式的各類精彩內容。至於「ATV亞洲電視App」的詳情如何，則有待亞洲電視之後的詳情公佈。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n來源：亞洲電視數碼媒體有限公司<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pc3mag.com/the-new-atv-coming/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fthe-new-atv-coming%2F&d=h2izqYTFbS8OV0hfSYxxTxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=7db41fa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pc3mag.com/the-new-atv-coming/</a>"},{"pid":"4d38560473d8258e02e56c999ad7babad05b8317","tid":497017,"uid":1174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陳展鵬可以回家了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783dac60d24d952909e179a0d2dea49b7fce175f","tid":497017,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:07:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陳展鵬可以回家了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n煎Pan難d<br />\n林韋辰果d死返過去啦, 額頭刻住「老土」兩個字"}]}